vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 1 to exercise the first of two, one-year renewal options with CitySquare to the service price agreement for housing and service assistance to homeless young adults ages 18 to 24 for the Office of Homeless Solutions for the period September 1, 2023 to August 31, 2024 - Not to exceed $242,731.00 - Financing: FY 2024 TDHCA-Homeless Housing and Services Program 23-24 Grant Funds (subject to annual appropriations)
